      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Great news @everyone! \n\nRun #2 (https://www.crowdsupply.com/wafer-space/gf180mcu-run-2/) has ***already*** surpassed that of Run #1 (https://www.crowdsupply.com/wafer-space/gf180mcu-run-1/) in every way -- number of backers, number of slots, and total committed funds!\n\nThis means that wafer.space runs are trending in the right direction and towards being cost neutral and thus sustainable and providing continued access to GF180MCU in the long term!",
