      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "We cut a microscopic wire inside a chip with an ion beam, then brought it back to life with platinum gas!\n\nMy latest video is a collaboration with Mikhail from ZeptoBars  \u2013 the only person I know to own a FIB (focussed ion beam) equipped electron microscope.\n\nI\u2019m releasing it as a youtube premiere at 18:00 CEST on Tuesday 12th May. Join me to watch it together, chat and ask questions in the comments.\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=plcgYPm3h9A",
